{
  "stem": "20088.9",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, he would never have gone back on his word.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then, by then I was very happy here, And I don't think I would have wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I'd gone through so many countries and, you know, languages and countries.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I felt quite at home here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I said to him then I would want to go to another country, start again with a different language.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So-- so that was-- that was that then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And Zvi's mother still lived in Israel, but she went then to Germany, partly as well to be nearer us, but as well because she got German repatriation money.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And-- and another bad thing first happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I went to-- I did work a bit as a photographer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But it was difficult to get jobs then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And so I did freelance photography.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I looked at all the adverts and did find a job.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then, in my spare time, I went to different museums for lectures.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There were free lectures.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I was very interested in-- that was geology.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And once, at a break, I met a man who said he does palm reading.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And could he read my palm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he read my palm, and he said, you-- you will have great difficulty getting children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You might not even get children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And that-- I was terribly upset about that, because like I told you, I thought to live is continuing with a family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I was-- and he told me all kind of things, which were true.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But this shocked me terribly, and a said to my husband-- were were only young married, and we-- he earned 10 pounds.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He had finished his-- his lecture.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he was a stockbroker, and he earned very little.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And we really were very poor.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
